https://openai.com
. We use ChatGPT for the following tools:
Chatbot
When a chat is started via the website or the admin area, the entries and the first name are transmitted to the OpenAI servers and processed there to generate a suitable response.
We have configured OpenAI so that the personal data entered is not used to train OpenAI's algorithm.
The use of OpenAI is based on Art. 6 para. 1 lit. f GDPD. The website operator has a legitimate interest in the most efficient customer communication possible using modern technical solutions. If a corresponding consent has been requested, the processing is carried out exclusively on the basis of Art. 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPD and § 25 para. 1 TTDSG. Consent can be revoked at any time.
Further information is available here:
https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy.
